rsion spells (ie: lich) to convert into mana. <br>     Engraved bone pauldrons are achieved through a very easy 30 minute quest and run under 400pp generally, acrylia is harder to obtain because its new, but at 45 you could take down the mobs for the tailoring components easy and turn in the components to your local tailor and maybe suppliment them with some cash to create these nice shoulders for you.<br>     I hope this info and my terrible english have helped some, I'd recommend looking for these mantles as they are all (minus jade/absorbtion) fairly easy to obtain. </p>&nbsp;<br>"A stranger is a friend you just haven't met yet"<br>60th Virtuoso of Povar</td></tr>
